headline: Happy Belly Food Group Signs National Distributional Agreement with Sysco
summary: Toronto, Ontario--(Newsfile Corp. - January 17, 2025) - Happy Belly Food Group Inc. (CSE: HBFG) (OTCQB: HBFGF) ("Happy Belly" or the "Company"), a leading consolidator of emerging food brands is pleased to announce that it has secured a national food distribution agreement with Sysco (NYSE: SYY), the global leader in selling, marketing and distributing food and related products to customers who prepare meals away from home.
